    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Software\" title=\"Software\">Software</a> * <a href=\"/Utilities\" title=\"Utilities\">Utilities</a> * InBetween</b>\n</p><p><b>InBetween</b>,<br />\na <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> <a href=\"/CLI\" title=\"CLI\">command line</a> utility written by <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a> that can be used to translate or modify text <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Command_(computing)\">commands</a> between <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Client_(computing)\">client</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Server_(computing)\">server</a>, for instance between a chess <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> (client) and <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">CECP</a> or <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">engine</a> (server) to fix communication incompatibilities or glitches in <a href=\"/Protocols\" title=\"Protocols\">protocol</a> implementations. Further, to track down possible incompatibilities, or for <a href=\"/Debugging\" title=\"Debugging\">debug</a> purpose <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, InBetween allows <a href=\"/Logging\" title=\"Logging\">logging</a> of all the communication between GUI and engine (client, server or both), either as output to the console or optionally written into a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Log_file\">log file</a>. Along with <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PuTTY\">PuTTY</a>, InBetween may be used for fusing a Windows GUI, such as <a href=\"/ChessBase_(Database)\" title=\"ChessBase (Database)\">ChessBase</a> to a chess engine on a <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a> server via a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Secure_Shell\">Secure Shell</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Engines\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Engines</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Postings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Postings</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Chess_Utility\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Utility</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Engines\">Engines</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=InBetween&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Engines\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Category:UCI\" title=\"Category:UCI\">UCI Engines</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Category:WinBoard\" title=\"Category:WinBoard\">WinBoard Engines</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Category:XBoard\" title=\"Category:XBoard\">XBoard Engines</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=InBetween&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Debugging\" title=\"Debugging\">Debugging</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Square_Attacked_By#InBetween\" title=\"Square Attacked By\">In Between Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Logging\" title=\"Logging\">Logging</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Protocols\" title=\"Protocols\">Protocols</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/UCI2WB\" title=\"UCI2WB\">UCI2WB</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Wb2UCI\" title=\"Wb2UCI\">Wb2UCI</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Postings\">Postings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=InBetween&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Postings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=InBetween&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=174723\">Last message&#160;:-), InBetween 1.1 by Odd Gunnar Malin is available&#160;!</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 11, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=33973\">Odd Gunnar Malin teaches how to run winboard Sos under ChessBase GUI</a> by Antonio Senatore, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 14, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=35904\">Inbetween debug output saving as a log file?</a> by <a href=\"/G%C3%BCnther_Simon\" title=\"Günther Simon\">Günther Simon</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 25, 2002</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=35904&amp;p=136087#p136093\">Re: Inbetween debug output saving as a log file?</a> by <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 26, 2002</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=43496\">Wb2UCI and Problems with ExChess4.03a and GnuChess4.0.8</a> by <a href=\"/Arturo_Ochoa\" title=\"Arturo Ochoa\">Arturo Ochoa</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, July 24, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/EXchess\" title=\"EXchess\">EXchess</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess\" title=\"GNU Chess\">GNU Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=311552\">inbetween log with majestic chess</a> by <a href=\"/Michael_Byrne\" title=\"Michael Byrne\">Mike Byrne</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 16, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Majestic_Chess\" title=\"Majestic Chess\">Majestic Chess</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=InBetween&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32927\">InBetween for Linux</a> by <a href=\"/Miguel_A._Ballicora\" title=\"Miguel A. Ballicora\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chess.com/blog/AldoE/the-tale-of-the-lost-wrapper-inbetween-by-odd-gunnar-malin\">The Tale of the Lost Wrapper: InBetween by Odd Gunnar Malin</a> by  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chess.com/members/view/AldoE\">Aldo Ercolani</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chess.com&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chess.com (page does not exist)\">Chess.com</a>, December 12, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55681\">Just Crafty GUI acept my 4 words UCI engine.... why?</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Luis_Babboni&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Luis Babboni (page does not exist)\">Luis Babboni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 16, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66366\">Debugging UCI engine</a> by Cadel Watson, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 19, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Debugging\" title=\"Debugging\">Debugging</a>, <a href=\"/Category:UCI\" title=\"Category:UCI\">UCI Engines</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=InBetween&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Utility\">Chess Utility</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=InBetween&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Utility\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20120717105032/http://home.online.no/~malin/sjakk/\">Chess and Data</a> by <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a>, hosted by the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">WaybackMachine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://adamsccpages.blogspot.de/p/computer-chess-utility-programs.html#i\">Adam's Computer Chess Pages: Computer Chess Utility Programs - InBetween</a> by <a href=\"/Adam_Hair\" title=\"Adam Hair\">Adam Hair</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://komodochess.com/remote-engine.htm\">Connecting a Windows box to a remote Engine on a GNU+Linux server</a> from <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">komodochess.com</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=InBetween&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/inbetween\">inbetween - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/in-between\">in-between - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/in_between\">in between - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inbetweening\">Inbetweening from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Category:Flat_Earth_Society\" title=\"Category:Flat Earth Society\">Flat Earth Society</a>  - In Between Rivers, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_F._Kennedy_Center_for_the_Performing_Arts\">John F. Kennedy Center for the Performing Arts</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Washington,_D.C.\">Washington D.C.</a>, 2011, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/U_58Jm-JiiI?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=InBetween&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=35904&amp;p=136087#p136093\">Re: Inbetween debug output saving as a log file?</a> by <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboar